@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam linetype ortho
skinparam nodesep 45
skinparam ranksep 40

title Iteracion 5 - Vista simplificada

class CircleUI {
  +UpdateSelectionHudDisplay()
  +UpdateVitalsHudDisplay()
}

class PauseMenuController {
  +TogglePause()
}

class Player {
  +TrySwapForm()
}

class PlayerStats {
  +GetFinalDamage()
  +GetSelectedWeaponId()
}

class PlayerCombatController {
  +TryAttack()
}

class WeaponDefinition

class MeleeHitbox {
  +Initialize()
}

class Projectile {
  +Initialize()
}

class DamageSourceContext {
  +Configure()
}

class EnemyController {
  +Configure()
  +ActivateAI()
  +ModifyIncomingDamage()
}

class EnemyHealth {
  +TakeDamage()
}

class EnemyProjectile {
  +Initialize()
}

class Room {
  +OnPlayerEnter()
  +OnEnemyDestroyed()
}

CircleUI --> Player : muestra forma activa
CircleUI --> PlayerStats : muestra arma y vida

Player --> PlayerStats : comparte estado
PlayerCombatController --> Player : obtiene forma/direccion
PlayerCombatController --> PlayerStats : calcula dano final
PlayerCombatController --> WeaponDefinition : selecciona arma
PlayerCombatController --> MeleeHitbox : genera ataque melee
PlayerCombatController --> Projectile : genera proyectil

MeleeHitbox --> DamageSourceContext : conserva contexto
Projectile --> DamageSourceContext : conserva contexto

MeleeHitbox --> EnemyHealth : aplica dano
Projectile --> EnemyHealth : aplica dano

EnemyHealth --> EnemyController : consulta resistencias
EnemyController --> Player : persigue / ataca
EnemyController --> EnemyProjectile : dispara
EnemyController --> Room : notifica muerte

PauseMenuController --> CircleUI : pausa la interfaz

@enduml
